subject: Soccer
Women's World Cup (Soccer)
organizations: United States Women's National Soccer Team
lead_paragraph: Rapinoe and Holiday — half of the team’s starting midfield — each picked up their second yellow card of the tournament on Monday, leading to suspensions for the game Friday against China.
